rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Woodboards! Woodboards!
The latest trend is Woodboards!

rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Using Superbia's cutting-edge technology,
we've created an instrument by processing our proud
Gulan Puzzletree Wood to its limits!

rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0003
rows.name:
It brings out the maximum flexibility of
Puzzletree Wood, and the sound it produces
is like the voice of an angel...

rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0004
rows.name:
And its name is the Woodboard!
I named it myself, by the way!

rows.label: tlk41400021_04_msg0005
rows.name:
It's a keyboard made of wood, so it's a Woodboard!
Get it? Wood! Board!
